472
00:36:10,060 --> 00:36:13,180
- Those two right there... Stole my wallet! 
 - There they are.

473
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:19,500
What's going on?

474
00:36:20,604 --> 00:36:22,264
Chubby?

475
00:36:23,532 --> 00:36:25,313
Master! Luo!

476
00:36:25,313 --> 00:36:27,061
What's happening here?

477
00:36:27,061 --> 00:36:28,902
It's rough...

478
00:36:28,902 --> 00:36:33,988
Master. Even though I'm here and I still don't know who our sect's examiner is,

479
00:36:33,988 --> 00:36:38,680
you and Grandmaster must've seen how well I've done.

480
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:41,901
I passed the trial, right?

481
00:36:41,901 --> 00:36:43,681
 Is that from Luo? 

482
00:36:44,935 --> 00:36:46,635
 Well... 

483
00:36:47,498 --> 00:36:48,979
 I'm getting off at the next stop. 

484
00:36:48,979 --> 00:36:50,564
 You ride it all the way to Yun Ridge. 

485
00:36:50,564 --> 00:36:52,685
 We'll pick you up once you're there. 

486
00:36:52,685 --> 00:36:54,325
 Wait, what for? 

487
00:36:57,594 --> 00:36:59,995
 It's part of your trial. 

488
00:36:59,995 --> 00:37:01,695
 A trial? 

489
00:37:33,786 --> 00:37:37,747
 You two can only swap it. 

490
00:37:37,747 --> 00:37:41,988
 If you let me join you, the Three Shell Game will be more fun! 

491
00:37:43,861 --> 00:37:45,841
 A pro, huh? 

492
00:37:46,905 --> 00:37:50,026
 Well, you want to join us? 

493
00:37:50,026 --> 00:37:53,571
 If it were two years ago, maybe I'd have joined in. 

494
00:37:53,571 --> 00:37:57,956
 But now, I only join righteous sects. 

495
00:37:57,956 --> 00:38:00,160
 Thieves! Officers! Him too! 

496
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:01,720
 - That one! 
 - Get down! 

497
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:04,780
 Train police! Over here! 

498
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:05,980
 Train police! 

499
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,810
Not bad!

500
00:38:07,810 --> 00:38:08,971
Good job.

501
00:38:08,971 --> 00:38:11,119
Oh, right. Thirteen-Thousand texted me.

502
00:38:11,119 --> 00:38:12,980
He's getting to Lixi tonight.

503
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:16,506
He said my chick won't shut up, and he couldn't deal with it.

504
00:38:16,506 --> 00:38:18,347
I'd better give it a name quickly.

505
00:38:18,347 --> 00:38:20,347
Any suggestions?

506
00:38:21,020 --> 00:38:23,514
Spicy Stir-fried Chicken!

507
00:38:23,514 --> 00:38:26,775
- Hop in the car. 
 - Wait, that's a dish, not a name.

508
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:31,545
If you name it that, won't it get some kind of trauma?

509
00:38:31,545 --> 00:38:33,348
It's a chicken. What else is it for?

510
00:38:33,348 --> 00:38:38,380
Naming it that is just a way to remind it to behave itself.

511
00:38:40,722 --> 00:38:42,500
Or how about Free Cao? What do you think?

512
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:43,760
Free Cao?

513
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:45,481
Same as me, you know?

514
00:38:45,481 --> 00:38:47,762
I took some wrong turns before.

515
00:38:47,762 --> 00:38:51,980
But thanks to you, I pulled back just in time and found my way again.

516
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:54,909
Now I'm free, my body, soul, everything.

517
00:38:54,909 --> 00:38:56,509
Free.

518
00:38:57,140 --> 00:38:58,760
I like it.

519
00:38:59,530 --> 00:39:01,670
All right, that's the name then.

520
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:23,400
Brother Luo.

